    <p>Amid the pan­demic’s job cuts, there has been a call to pro­tect the Sin­ga­porean core. In­sight looks at the chal­lenges fac­ing the cit­i­zen worker.</p>
    <p>As Covid-19 takes a toll on the labour mar­ket, there have been calls to pro­tect and strengthen the Sin­ga­porean core and help lo­cals level up amid com­pe­ti­tion from for­eign tal­ent. How has the pro­file of the Sin­ga­pore worker evolved over the years? What are his core strengths, the con­cerns over his ca­pa­bil­i­ties, and the chal­lenges he faces? In­sight re­ports.</p>

